name: Nord Sample Editor Project
summary: An NSMPPROJ file is a Nord Sample Editor project file. It contains metadata used to load a Nord Sample Editor project. For example, an NSMPPROJ file contains a reference to the audio files included in a user's project. It does not contain any actual audio data.

open.note: Open with an associated app listed below.
